	   <tr><td colspan=2>I'd suggest making a Half Elf or Wood Elf and put all your skill points into STA and a few into STR(STA becomes rather important and is one of the more difficult stats to raise.)  If you have 500pp to spend, get a suit of banded and a set of icetooth claws and a piercing weapon or 1hb.  Songs dont cost a terrible amount as you only get one a level usually.  Cheers.<br><br>-Trino<br>--55 Bard of The Rathe<br>-Google<br>--32 Warrior of The Rathe<br>-West<br>--39 Wiz of Tunare<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
