	   <tr><td colspan=2>I would be very careful about going overweight due to your armour.  It severly limits how much you can loot without returning to a shop to sell.  Although there are several songs that will boost your strength, if you have to rely on one of these not to be encumbered you will limit your options.  For example, when you get to lvl 12, you will get a fairly good DD song (Brusco's Bellow) if you are up against a caster you will probably want to twist it with Elemental Rhythms, trying to add a strength song into the twist at these levels may just be too much.  The +5 saves might be nice, but up to now (lvl 15) I've not had too much problem with either.  I would sell the armour and get something lighter.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
